"text\",\n              \"text\": \"**Silent ‚Äî no report.**\\n\\nComparing current state (23:54 UTC) against baseline from `heartbeat-state.json` (17:35 UTC):\\n\\n| Session | Baseline | Current | Œî |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| `cron:6f3323ef` | running ‚úÖ | running ‚úÖ | ‚Äî |\\n| `cron:e7885813` | running ‚úÖ | running ‚úÖ | ‚Äî (new clean instance cycling normally) |\\n| `telegram:group:-5163901258` | running ‚úÖ | running ‚úÖ | ‚Äî |\\n| `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV monitor) | ‚Äî | running ‚úÖ | New, but child sessions completed cleanly (normal lifecycle) |\\n\\nNo new failures, no blockers, no unexpected state changes. Pipeline: **HEALTHY**.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 365,\n            \"output\": 632,\n            \"totalTokens\": 44586,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14264,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 29325,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776210888280,\n          \"responseId\": \"062e06c9af520d1c6bafc9e383ad7f3c\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"60d22577\",\n            \"seq\": 7\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776210790377,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"c