nt":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the baseline state from heartbeat-state.json (last check at 17:35 UTC = 00:35 UTC+7 on Apr 15):\n\n**Baseline (17:35 UTC):**\n- `cron:6f3323ef`: running ‚úÖ\n- `cron:e7885813`: running ‚úÖ (clean instance)\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258`: running ‚úÖ\n\n**Current (23:54 UTC):**\nFrom sessions_list, the running sessions are:\n- `cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31` (5p DTLX Monitor) ‚Äî running ‚úÖ ‚Äî updatedAt: 1776210663001 (~23:43 UTC)\n\n\n- `cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e` (Agent Status to Lead) ‚Äî running ‚úÖ ‚Äî updatedAt: 1776210680671 (~23:44 UTC) ‚Äî started ~22:51 UTC, so it's been cycling through new instances every 5 minutes\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7` (5p QLHV Monitor) ‚Äî running ‚úÖ ‚Äî updatedAt: 1776210627463\n\nAll the baseline sessions are still running as expected, so nothing's changed from the previous check. I should stay silent since there's nothing to report. The cron:e7885813 session is also running with an Agent Status to Lead task, though it appears to have ended earlier at 22:03 UTC before a new instance started around 22:51 UTC. Both the 5p QLHV Monitor and 5p DTLX Monitor are running as expected, and the overall pipeline status is HEALTHY. Checking the session list more carefully, I see 39 total sessions including the running crons and the group monitor, with several done or failed sessions that appear to be historical. Comparing against the baseline, the same sessions are still running‚Äîcron:6f3323ef, cron:e7885813, and telegram:group:-5163901258‚Äîso there's been no change. The system is stable with no failures or blockers, so I'll stay silent as instructed."},{"type":"text","text":"**Silent ‚Äî no report.**\n\nComparing current state (23:54 UTC) against baseline from `heartbeat-state.json` (17:35 UTC):\n\n| Session | Baseline | Current | Œî |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| `cron:6f3323ef` | running ‚úÖ | running ‚úÖ | ‚Äî |\n| `cron:e7885813` | running ‚úÖ | running ‚úÖ | ‚Äî (new clean instance cycling normally) |\n| `telegram:group:-5163901258` | running ‚úÖ | running ‚úÖ | ‚Äî |\n| `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV monitor) | ‚Äî | running ‚úÖ | New, but child sessions completed cleanly (normal lifecycle) |\n\nNo new failures, no blockers, no unexpected state changes. Pipeline: **HEALTHY**."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":365,"output":632,"totalTokens":44586,"cacheRead":14264,"cacheWrite":29325,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776210888280,"responseId":"062e06c9af520d1c6bafc9e383ad7f3c","__openclaw":{"id":"60d22577","seq":7}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776210790377,"sessionId":"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":55428,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776162044660,"endedAt":1776162158012,"runtimeMs":113352,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134","lastAccountId":"main_bot","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"23:42 UTC = 06:42 UTC+7, within quiet hours (23:00-07:00). Silent heartbeat."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":142,"output":37,"totalTokens":55259,"cacheRead":7778,"cacheWrite":47302,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776210201148,"responseId":"062e041a8e2194436d31b0fc3ef4b890","__openclaw":{"id":"5b5015cf","seq":1411}},{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"üåê Orbis ‚Äî Agent Status | 23:51 UTC 14 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 3\n‚Ä¢ cron:ed2d0b5d: running ‚Äî 5p QLHV Monitor (3 child sessions) ‚Äî ~1h 49m\n‚Ä¢ cron:6f3323ef: running ‚Äî 5p DTLX Monitor ‚Äî ~3h 5m\n‚Ä¢ telegram:group:-5163901258: running ‚Äî QLHV ecosystem group ‚Äî ~2h 5m\n\nPipeline: HEALTHY ‚úÖ\n‚Ä¢ MCP: stitch ‚úÖ confluence ‚úÖ gitlab ‚úÖ\n‚Ä¢ Blockers: none\n\n‚Äî Orbis üåê"}],"timestamp":1776210783485,"provenance":{"kind":"inter_session","sourceSessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","sourceTool":"sessions_send"},"__openclaw":{"id":"5a87b197","seq":1412}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Same pattern - just heartbeat status reports. Silent acknowledgment."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":225,"output":20,"totalTokens":55448,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":55203,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776210783630,"responseId":"062e0661682f6f695362824a7069af5b","__openclaw":{"id":"f2ce90c5","seq":1413}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: Agent Status to Lead","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1776210680671,"sessionId":"bfb30e26-86f2-4977-84ee-30b76966327b","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":25499,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776208475547,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/bfb30e26-86f2-4977-84ee-30b76966327b.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the full picture. Let me analyze all the active master-orchestrator sessions (excluding this cron session `cron:e7885813-0446-4101-a171-941c2416848e`):\n\n1. **agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7** ‚Äî status: running, started: ~22:02 UTC (startedAt: 1776207735553), last update: 1776210627463 (~22:43 UTC). Label: \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\". Has 3 child sessions. Running ~1h 49m.\n\n\n2. **agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31** ‚Äî status: running, started: ~05:25 UTC (startedAt: 1776199558073), last update: 1776210540062 (~22:29 UTC). Label: \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\". Running ~2h 6m.\n3. **agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258** ‚Äî status: running, started: ~03:03 UTC (startedAt: 1776162044660), last update: 1776210112732 (~22:21 UTC). Running ~19h 48m.\n4. **agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134** ‚Äî status: done. The last message was the status report at 23:41 UTC.\n5. **agent:master-orchestrator:main** ‚Äî status: done.\n6. **agent:master-orchestrator:cron:53c5832a** ‚Äî status: done (no status field, but no status:\"running\" either).\n\nNow I'm recalculating the durations more carefully by working backwards from the current timestamp of 1776210694251 to figure out exactly when each session started.\n\nThe cron:e7885813 session just started itself at 23:51 UTC, so it's running but I should exclude it. That leaves three active sessions: the QLHV progress report cron that's been running for about 49 minutes, the DTLX progress report cron that's been active for roughly 3 hours, and the Telegram group channel that's been going for around 2 hours.\n\nLooking at the timing more carefully, I'm realizing the cron job sends updates every 5 minutes, but the last actual status report to Telegram was at 23:41 UTC‚Äîwhich means the 5-minute cycle should have triggered another update around 23:46, though I'm not seeing that in the logs.\n\nSince the cron:e7885813 session just started at 23:51 UTC, it's about 10 minutes old and appears to be one of the monitoring cron jobs. I'm checking the timestamps on the other cron sessions to understand the pattern‚Äîthe older ones ran at 23:49 and 23:49 UTC, but this one is fresh, so it seems like the system is cycling through multiple cron jobs throughout the hour.\n\nLooking at the running sessions now: the QLHV Progress Report cron started around 22:02 UTC and has been active for about 1 hour 49 minutes, the DTLX Progress Report cron has been running for roughly 3 hours 5 minutes, and the Telegram group session started much earlier at around 16:03 UTC and is still going.\n\nSince the pipeline is healthy with no blockers, I should send HEARTBEAT_OK as the message indicates this is the signal to confirm everything's running smoothly. Looking at the timing of the previous cron cycle at 23:49 UTC and when the status report was sent to the Telegram direct session, I need to figure out the current cron:e7885813 cycle timing and when the next 5-minute report would be due. Since the most recent activity was a heartbeat at 23:41 UTC, I'm calculating whether we're still within the quiet hours or if it's time to send the next status update. I'm realizing the instruction doesn't explicitly define what constitutes a meaningful change‚Äîit just says to send HEARTBEAT_OK only if no other sessions are active. Since there are three other sessions running, I should send a status report rather than staying silent. Let me format the output as requested: the orb identifier, current timestamp, and a count of the active sessions.\n\nNow I'm pulli