ine is just the addition of the 5p QLHV monitor, which has been reporting its status regularly.\n\nThe system is stable with no new failures or blockers, so I should remain silent and not generate a report.","thinkingSignature":"90bbcf72f34516df34fcf408fc83e9dacdb3b0d12492aac3bd1eee8d478420ee"},{"type":"text","text":"Silent ‚Äî no report.\n\n**Baseline (17:35 UTC):** `cron:6f3323ef` ‚úÖ `cron:e7885813` ‚úÖ `telegram:group:-5163901258` ‚úÖ\n\n**Current (23:55 UTC):** Same 3 sessions + `cron:ed2d0b5d` (5p QLHV monitor) ‚úÖ ‚Äî all running. No new failures, no blockers. Pipeline: **HEALTHY**."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":365,"output":648,"cacheRead":14272,"cacheWrite":27344,"totalTokens":42629,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776210952108,"responseId":"062e0709d4c5bba32bdf2a17220a6fc8"}}
